<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/uk-visas-and-immigration> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "UK Visas and Immigration (UKVI) is responsible for making millions of decisions every year about who has the right to visit or stay in the country, with a firm emphasis on national security and a culture of customer satisfaction for people who come here legally. UKVI is part of the Home Office ."@en .
